, Lightroom Classic, and 1TB of cloud storage for accessing and editing photos anywhere, and the Creative Cloud Photography plan includes Lightroom, Lightroom Classic, Photoshop, and 1TB of cloud storage. Compare photography plan pricing and features.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      \n        Can I try the Adobe photography plans before I buy them?\n      \n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes, you can try the Adobe photography plans by downloading a free seven-day trial of Adobe Creative Cloud to see if it’s right for you. Start free trial","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      \n        Do I need to be online to use the Adobe Creative Cloud apps?\n      \n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"No. All of your Creative Cloud desktop apps are installed directly on your computer, and you don’t need an internet connection to run them.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      \n        Where do I go if I need more information about photography plans?\n      \n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Read the full FAQ about all the photography plans to help you pick the perfect one for you. Learn more about Creative Cloud photography plans.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      \n        What’s the difference between Photoshop and Lightroom?\n      \n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Although the two digital photography editing apps are similar, the main difference between Photoshop and Lightroom is that Photoshop specializes in image manipulation, creation, and enhancement, while Lightroom focuses on editing, organizing, and processing photos. Learn more about Photoshop versus Lightroom.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      \n        How much is the Creative Cloud Photography plan?\n      \n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The Creative Cloud Photography plan is  for the annual paid monthly plan or   for the annual prepaid plan. This plan includes Lightroom, Lightroom Classic, Photoshop, and 1TB of cloud storage. Compare photography plans and pricing.","@type":"Answer"}}]]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/css/layout.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/media/media.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-navigation/utilities/menu/menu.css"><link rel="preload" as="script" crossorigin="anonymous" href="/libs/blocks/merch-card/merch-card.js"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/merch-card/merch-card.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/css/popover.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/css/profile.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/rounded-corners.css"><style>
