        <div><div class="fragment" data-path="/cc-shared/fragments/creativecloud/photography/faqs"><div class="section xxl-spacing" data-has-placeholders="true">
  <div class="text center xs-spacing-bottom text-block con-block" data-block-status="loaded" daa-lh="b13|text|nopzn|photography">
    <div class="foreground">
      <div class="body-m">
        <h2 id="new-to-adobe-photography-we-have-answers" class="heading-xl">New to Adobe photography? We have answers.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-container seo max-width-12-desktop static-links con-block" data-block-status="loaded" daa-lh="b14|accordion-conta|nopzn|photography"><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What s the differenc">
      
        What’s the difference between the Adobe photography plans?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The difference between the Adobe photography plans is that the Lightroom plan includes Lightroom, Lightroom Classic, and 1TB of cloud storage for accessing and editing photos anywhere, and the Creative Cloud Photography plan includes Lightroom, Lightroom Classic, Photoshop, and 1TB of cloud storage. <a href="/creativecloud/photography/compare-plans/" daa-ll="Compare photography -2--What s the differenc">Compare photography plan pricing and features.</a></div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--Can I try the Adobe ">
      
        Can I try the Adobe photography plans before I buy them?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, you can try the Adobe photography plans by downloading a free seven-day trial of Adobe Creative Cloud to see if it’s right for you. <a is="checkout-link" data-checkout-workflow-step="segmentation" data-modal="twp" data-quantity="1" data-wcs-osi="tNF8YrqR3DslSda-1L6pK5z-nYWDQYnjdHkwFDjGAas" data-extra-options="{}" class="placeholder-resolved" href="https://commerce.adobe.com/store/segmentation?cli=mini_plans&amp;ctx=if&amp;co=US&amp;lang=en&amp;ms=COM&amp;ot=TRIAL&amp;cs=INDIVIDUAL&amp;pa=PA-128&amp;rtc=t&amp;lo=sl&amp;af=uc_new_user_iframe%2Cuc_new_system_close" data-modal-id="mini-plans-web-cta-photoshop-lightroom-classic-card" aria-label="Start free trial - Photography - Individuals" daa-ll="Start free trial-4--Can I try the Adobe "><span style="pointer-events: none;">Start free trial</span></a></div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--Do I need to be onli">
      
        Do I need to be online to use the Adobe Creative Cloud apps?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>No. All of your <a href="/creativecloud/all-apps/" daa-ll="Creative Cloud deskt-6--Do I need to be onli">Creative Cloud desktop apps</a> are installed directly on your computer, and you don’t need an internet connection to run them.</div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--Where do I go if I n">
      
        Where do I go if I need more information about photography plans?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Read the full FAQ about all the photography plans to help you pick the perfect one for you. <a href="https://helpx.adobe.com/creative-cloud/faq/CCPp.html?promoid=BRLW391X&amp;mv=other" daa-ll="Learn more about Cre-8--Where do I go if I n">Learn more about Creative Cloud photography plans.</a></div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--What s the differenc">
      
        What’s the difference between Photoshop and Lightroom?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Although the two digital photography editing apps are similar, the main difference between Photoshop and Lightroom is that Photoshop specializes in image manipulation, creation, and enhancement, while Lightroom focuses on editing, organizing, and processing photos. <a href="/creativecloud/photography/lightroom-vs-photoshop/" daa-ll="Learn more about Pho-10--What s the differenc">Learn more about Photoshop versus Lightroom.</a></div></div><div class="descr-term"><h3 class="accordion-heading"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--How much is the Crea">
      
        How much is the Creative Cloud Photography plan?
      
    <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></h3></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>The Creative Cloud Photography plan is <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-display-recurrence="true" data-display-tax="false" data-force-tax-exclusive="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="optical" data-wcs-osi="MzCpF9nUi8rEzyW-9slEUwtRenS69PRW5fp84a93uK4" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price price-optical"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">19</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">99</span><span class="price-recurrence">/mo</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span> for the annual paid monthly plan or <span is="inline-price" data-display-per-unit="false" data-quantity="1" data-template="annual" data-wcs-osi="Jevk0Gu6IXPweYd7ILN3HKhYabHTdJp2sIOeNUCLT5c" class="placeholder-resolved"><span class="price price-annual"><span class="price-currency-symbol">US$</span><span class="price-currency-space disabled"></span><span class="price-integer">239</span><span class="price-decimals-delimiter">.</span><span class="price-decimals">88</span><span class="price-recurrence">/yr</span><span class="price-unit-type disabled"></span><span class="price-tax-inclusivity disabled"></span></span></span>  for the annual prepaid plan. This plan includes Lightroom, Lightroom Classic, Photoshop, and 1TB of cloud storage. <a href="/creativecloud/photography/compare-plans/" daa-ll="Compare photography -12--How much is the Crea">Compare photography plans and pricing.</a></div></div></div></div>
